I thought the other boys
would bully me for it.

25
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:11,480
And they did.

26
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:16,480
They called me slurs, shoved me around,
made me scared to come to school.

27
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:20,240
