like I was the problem.

28
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,560
But I wasn't.

29
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,080
-He's got this.
-I know.

30
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:29,000
The problem was the culture of bullying
that existed in this school.

31
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:34,680
Guys often struggle with mental health
'cause we keep our feelings to ourselves.

32
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:38,840
We have to brush everything off as banter
and pretend we feel okay when we don't.

33
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,200
Pretend that being made fun of
or laughed at

34
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:45,800
or kicked or punched or whatever
isn't scary or upsetting or…

35
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,160
