985
00:55:29,880 --> 00:55:34,560
-[boy laughing]
-[boys chanting playfully]

986
00:55:35,200 --> 00:55:37,960
[electronic music continues]

987
00:55:43,760 --> 00:55:46,640
-[boy retching]
-[boys] Urgh! [laughing]

988
00:55:57,040 --> 00:55:59,280
-[Elle] Yeah.
-[Isaac] Shall we go outside for a bit?

989
00:55:59,360 --> 00:56:01,760
-[Charlie] I think he might be upstairs.
-Okay.

990
00:56:02,280 --> 00:56:04,480
[music thumping in distance]

991
00:56:12,640 --> 00:56:13,800
Hey.

992
00:56:14,440 --> 00:56:15,600
Did you wanna go?

993
00:56:16,280 --> 00:56:18,840
[exhales sharply] Yeah. Yeah, I guess.

994
00:56:18,920 --> 00:56:20,680
O… only if you want to.

995
00:56:22,160 --> 00:56:25,160
-It is a bit boring, isn't it? So…
-[chuckles] Yeah.

996
00:56:28,200 --> 00:56:29,240
Hey. Um…

997
00:56:31,800 --> 00:56:33,680
Are you angry at me about something?

998
00:56:33,760 --> 00:56:35,960
What? N… no.

999
00:56:37,120 --> 00:56:38,440
Why do you think that?

1000
00:56:38,520 --> 00:56:41,240
You've avoided me tonight.

1001
00:56:41,320 --> 00:56:42,720
I'm sorry, I…

1002
00:56:44,640 --> 00:56:47,040
I just wanted you
to have a good night, and…

1003
00:56:48,240 --> 00:56:51,880
You know, you, you probably wanna
talk to your friends about uni.

1004
00:56:52,800 --> 00:56:55,240
It's only, like, four months away now, so…

1005
00:56:57,080 --> 00:56:58,240
Sure. Um…

1006
00:57:00,040 --> 00:57:01,880
It's gonna be really hard
when you're not here.

1007
00:57:02,400 --> 00:57:04,920
[scoffs] No, you're…
you're gonna be great.

1008
00:57:05,000 --> 00:57:09,280
-You don't need me hanging around.
-It's still gonna be really hard.

1009
