What if everything just blows up,
like Tao and Elle?

1010
00:57:14,240 --> 00:57:16,800
[hesitates] I mean,
I guess that's possible.

1011
00:57:19,560 --> 00:57:21,560
I know you've been struggling this year.

1012
00:57:22,800 --> 00:57:26,040
You've been really anxious
about a lot of things, about yourself.

1013
