Yeah, sorry, I know
that's probably annoying for you.

1014
00:57:29,840 --> 00:57:33,360
It's not annoying. It's just… upsetting.

1015
00:57:34,000 --> 00:57:38,160
'Cause… [sighs] …I try and talk to you
about it, and you just shut down.

1016
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:40,880
And I thought we were good at that.

1017
00:57:43,080 --> 00:57:46,080
And I think that the reason you do that
is… is because of me.

1018
00:57:49,120 --> 00:57:52,080
Maybe it is a good idea
for us to have some space, you know?

1019
